Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.44,0:00:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.39,0:00:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是有戏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.95,0:00:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}喔 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.57,0:00:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.10,0:00:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.60,0:00:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,什么 什么 在聊什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.26,0:00:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,从男人那里收到什么礼物算有戏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.88,0:00:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我之前收到橡皮擦了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.06,0:00:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那只是妳考试忘记带 借妳用而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.42,0:00:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,没戏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.36,0:00:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我收到手机吊饰了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.75,0:00:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯...那算哪边呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.72,0:00:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,千代有收过什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.52,0:00:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.50,0:00:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.74,0:00:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我是...那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.44,0:00:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,签名...吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.72,0:00:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,快放弃吧 那种男人
